Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:49.17,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz270\pos(610,150)}好想讓你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:55.61,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz270\pos(610,150)}在那彼岸的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:22:01.49,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz270\pos(610,150)}你也應該知道風很大
